thread.title: Patricia Pickard

author: Patricia Pickard
title: Patricia Pickard
text: I was very pleased with the staff, they even greeted at the door. I had a request to have storage unit by door, and they didn't asked question of why. They offered boxes to ast. in move but didn't need. The explained everything down to the letter. They asked if we wanted a hard copy of engagement or email to save paper, and we had them email it to us.I will let my friends, and family know if they ever need to store thing to call SelfStorage.
